Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙  把自己国家的公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么  快抓起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把手上拿着的东西放下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就杀了你们的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是真的生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了我——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常生气了！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.49,0:01:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传令  传令——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停战命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经结束了吗  真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要更多地相互厮杀相互仇恨才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个领域  比至今感受过的都要强大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了  这么严重的污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么邪恶的领域的人除了他不会有别人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙就是灾祸的现主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是人类变成的凭魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却看不到人类的形体  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去吧  艾德娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让史雷死在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:55.78,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,1500)\blur2\pos(270.571,564.429)}灾祸的现主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的家伙能净化得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米克里欧  这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为导师净化你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾祸的现主！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙  竟敢对着我的主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我看看你的器量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要净化我  太自大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然出现了新的导师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡的预感  是很美妙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.28,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(627,652)}清净的莱拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗艾斯=梅玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自以为看得见别人看不到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得见所有地方都被污秽侵蚀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾祸的现主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷  这不是我们现在能赢得过的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  到我这里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,污秽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾祸的现主  你竟然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这些凭魔的污秽中活下来让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是人类的污秽  强大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了人类进行净化的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击的却正是人类的污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是毫无道理  让人愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终有一天可以把世界完全净化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有人类  这片大地的污秽就无穷尽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终有一天人类和天族共存的世界会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎  艾莉莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下  振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血止不住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救护班还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚找人去叫了  我去看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  战斗…停止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就去把史雷带来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师的话  导师的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死  公主
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好  还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主死了的话  下次该找谁玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这污秽太严重连我都难受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连海兰德的军队都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急让救护班过来  快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界正在走向何处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想打倒我的主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连主人的仆从都打不倒是根本不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受人类污秽的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的罪恶是无尽的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  赛蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去啊导师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成为人类的希望之后将由我来打败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对活在这世上的人没有比这更绝望的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能只依靠史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然比起导师我们能做的有限
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分散敌人还是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  又是你？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在更南边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去叫史雷的人那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就闭上嘴按我说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续向南走  去深处的悬崖边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这么严重的污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像全世界的污秽都集中在这个区域了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎终于结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别死在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事情要你帮我做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把史雷误认为导师  第一次遇见的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有分别时我说史雷适合做导师的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣剑祭上史雷成为导师的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:12:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在也记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说梦想是人类和天族和睦共处的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又让我重新觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的导师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是  史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——像你这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是史雷真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是  有艾莉莎在真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许因为最初遇见的人类是艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能相信自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回瑞迪雷克去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在前线的战斗很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的任务是为了不让战争爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在政治的世界战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让血再白流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎  和我交换从士的契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从士？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帮助艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不会给史雷增加负担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我变强就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我也拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我做你的从士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷  请接着我的咏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给予艾莉莎古代语的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄宿于吾之圣枝  萌生新芽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花结果  果成种
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮回的宿缘在此施放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻由导师赐名  作连理之证
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铭记吧  汝为导师从士的真名是——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「玛奥可丝=阿美卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「笑容的艾莉莎」的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么怎么  互相注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算上我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萝洁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我也要分别了吧  为什么只是史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  那么好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  真随便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感情真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  史雷也来握手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师  你想妨碍我兰登立功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登  你这样子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔托洛阁下看到你的人头的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会明白你和我谁才是国家需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是凭魔化的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷  就是这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤害了公主的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙把艾莉莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种不懂世故的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家是不需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就和导师一起除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家伙把艾莉莎的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以史雷！  不能被愤怒支配
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为有你这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界才…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷不行  史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为有你这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要被污秽吞没了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人由我带回瑞迪雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举行正式的裁决  由司法处置他的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你忍住了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  突然间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前欠我的人情  还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在打鬼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  不是要你在战争中站在哪一边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来在洛伦斯有交易
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能一起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交涉对象是个比较麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想有导师在的话交涉也会顺利的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也预定要去洛伦斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给史雷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  就和萝洁一起去洛伦斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  这样就互不相欠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  那家伙在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙就是那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的话在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也许意外地很淘气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎会很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  出发吧！
